extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed based on a tutorial from the Mozilla Developer Network.


  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else

    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] !{bookCount}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{bookInstanceCount}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{bookInstanceAvailableCount} 
      li #[strong Authors:] !{authorCount}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{genreCount}